          window.googletag.pubads().addEventListener('slotRenderEnded', function(event) {
            if (event.isEmpty) {
              return;
            }
            var list = document.documentElement.classList;
            var size = event.size[0]+ 'x' + event.size[1];
            var isBannerTop = event.slot.getSlotElementId() === 'banner_top_0';
            var isBannerSize = size === '728x90';
            var hasClass = /cns-has-banner-top-size-728x90$/.test(list);
            if (isBannerTop && !hasClass && isBannerSize) {
              document.documentElement.classList = list + ' cns-has-banner-top-size-' + size;
            }
          });
